- content_for :title do
  = t('admin2.sidebar.payment_system.country_currency')

.content-card-header
  %h1.content-card-header-title
    = t('admin2.sidebar.payment_system.country_currency')

.content-card-section-container
  %section.content-card-section
    %h2
      = t('admin2.sidebar.payment_system.country_currency')

    %form.content-card-section-form
      .form-group
        %label{:for => "country"} Country
        %input#country.form-control{"aria-describedby" => "country", :disabled => "disabled", :placeholder => "Finland", :type => "text"}/
        %small#country-help.form-text
          Want to change the country of your marketplace?
          = succeed "." do
            %a{:href => "#"} Contact the Sharetribe team
      .form-group
        %label{:for => "currency"} Currency
        %select#currency.form-control{"aria-describedby" => "currency"}
          %option Euro - â‚¬ - EUR
          %option US Dollar - $ - USD
          %option British pound - Â£ - GBP
          %option More currencies - More currencies - More currencies

  %section.content-card-section
    %h2 Available payment gateways
    %p.ingress
      Based on your country and currency settings,
      %strong PayPal
      and
      %strong Stripe
      can be configured as payment gateways in your marketplace.
    %p.ingress
      VARIATION - Based on your country and currency settings,
      %strong PayPal
      can be configured as payment gateway in your marketplace.
    %p.ingress VARIATION - Based on your country and currency settings, there is unfortunately no payment gateways available in your marketplace.
    %p
      You can learn more about the availability of payment gateways, for country, in the following articles:
    %ul
      %li
        %a{:href => "https://help.sharetribe.com/en/articles/666091", :target => "_blank"} Countries and currencies supported by PayPal
      %li
        %a{:href => "https://help.sharetribe.com/en/articles/1063017", :target => "_blank"} Countries and currencies supported by Stripe
  .content-card-terminal.without-margin
    %a.btn.btn-primary{:href => "#"} Save changes
